                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180218-90-off474 t18180218-90-crimeloc477"></join>. On the 7th of February, the shoes were cut from my door, where they hung. I heard them rattle-ran out, and saw the prisoner putting them under his coat; I secured him, and took them from him.</p>
